{"tid":1358450,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家都知政府係唔會回應民意","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T10:15:52.000Z","uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c55c63f82fa47910aebf549422dc77d54fc72df7","tid":1358450,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:34:18.000Z","msg":"政府係唔會回應跪求，亦唔會俾你人多聲大嚇到，因為佢碌炮大，根本唔放你在眼內。<br />\n<br />\n而家就好似困係原有出口已經坍塌嘅山洞入面，面前路有兩條：<br />\n1. 遊行示威係一條艱難嘅路，亦係一條不停兜圈嘅路。<br />\n2. _ _ 革命係一條九死一生、遙遙無期嘅不歸路，但唯一出口就係個邊，可能去到自己曾孫個代會到達出口，亦可能未到出口就全軍覆沒。<br />\n<br />\n結論：一係坐定定慳力氣等死，一係就抱住犧牲嘅準備行條出路。<br />\n<br />\n冇話邊條路係好啲，有人珍惜生命，亦有人視死如歸，每日價值觀唔同先係正常。<br />\n即使目前唔會成事，日後嘅成功必須建基於往日嘅屢敗屢戰，中外歷史一直講緊呢個道理。近代中國有孫中山佢地做例子，現代西方有烏克蘭做例子。"},{"pid":"73515ef1a87adb649e1ba0b0078ca61ffd47e9d8","tid":1358450,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"903f853e181fb860ce6ab85a4a799f2838ef7307","tid":1358450,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a5625407b4eb1c735cde8661d0f7abb11a4dde9c","tid":1358450,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64edfe6183cc7203e9eeb8b305c9e2baf531ec2","tid":1358450,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a26817051907752dcfc59a2094351510c3d804","tid":1358450,"uid":260325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:19:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bd3797624cc1c7331c87d723dc7dc399cc51fba","tid":1358450,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}